<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 57, 130);"><strong>A positive comment does not necessarily mean it is constructive.&nbsp;</strong></span></h2>

<h2 style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgb(85, 57, 130);"><strong>Some comments might have characteristics of both constructive and &nbsp;non-constructive comments. &nbsp;</strong><br><strong>Use your judgement to decide which characteristics weigh more in such cases.</strong></span></h2>

